> Management overview of Linux scalability at webserving:
> 
> CPU	Score	Scaling
> 1	1270	100%
> 2	2200	86.6%
> 4	4200	82.7%
> 8	6387	62.9%
> 
> Management overview of NT scalability at webserving:
> 
> CPU	Score	Scaling
> 1	732	100%
> 4	1598	54.6%
> 
